
fg    -- gEnable Helpterminal Status g-------------------------------------------

    You have just enabled your HelpTerminal status. You have been marked with
    a 'r?g' in the wholist. To send x-es marked as HelpTerminal, type 'cSYSGUIDEg'
    by itself on the first line of the eXpress message. To disabled HelpTerm
    status, press w<r%w>g once more.

